# a14 = Artist.create(url: "http://static.wixstatic.com/media/60db4a_774a31eb4d094503a6afab88d9de8d5a.jpg_srz_p_497_686_75_22_0.50_1.20_0.00_jpg_srz", first_name: "Gabrielle", last_name: "Viertel", artist_description: "Gabrielle Viertel is a German artist and photographer based in the Netherlands. She studied design and technology and has been completely devoted to photography since 2011 as a fulltime artist. In a magical and surreal way, the artist's photographic work transcends the boundaries between performance and documentation. Her artworks are characterized by delicate femininity, the beauty of colors and shapes as well as human vulnerability. She captures scenes from an almost unreal world or stills straight out of a dream. Gabrielle Viertel's expressive underwater art and fashion photography often conveys a touch of darkness with a mysterious flair. She is conserving the elegance of classical photography with the addition of surrealistic elements. As a lover of performing arts, the artist stages every work meticulously and choreographically.")
